OL,3,CThe collapse of Welsh rugby: From
OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,F2019 was a year when the golden
OL,7,Fgeneration peaked - a Grand Slam, an
OL,8,Fascent to No.1 in the world and a
OL,9,FWorld Cup quest filled with hope and
OL,10,Fexpectation.
OL,12,FThere had been record levels of
OL,13,Freinvestment in the game in Wales.
OL,14,FThings hadn't been this good since the
OL,15,Fglory days of the 1970s.
OL,17,FBut fast forward to the present day,
OL,18,Fand the differences could not be more
OL,19,Fstark.
