OL,3,CThe collapse of Welsh rugby: From
OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,FWales are now 11th in the world, their
OL,7,Flowest ever ranking. After years of
OL,8,Flurching from one crisis to the next,
OL,9,Fthe Welsh Rugby Union is now pressing
OL,10,Fahead with plans to reduce the number
OL,11,Fof professional sides from four to
OL,12,Fthree.
OL,14,FThe hope being that consolidating
OL,15,Flimited finances and a dwindling
OL,16,Fplayer pool will reverse fortunes.
OL,18,FBut the rapid decline raises one
OL,19,Fburning question - how on earth did
OL,20,FWales, a once great empire of world
OL,21,Frugby, crumble to such an extent?
