OL,3,CThe collapse of Welsh rugby: From
OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,FITV Wales has produced a documentary -
OL,7,F'Laughing Stock': The Collapse of
OL,8,FWelsh Rugby - to explore just what has
OL,9,Fgone wrong.
OL,11,FFinancially Unsustainable
OL,13,FThe Coronavirus pandemic brought the
OL,14,Fworld to a screeching halt, and that
OL,15,Fincluded sports.
OL,17,FWhen games eventually returned, there
OL,18,Fwere no fans, no ticket sales, no
OL,19,Fmoney being spent in the club shop, no
OL,20,Ffood and beverage profit.
