OL,6,FA vast majority of income dried up
OL,7,Fovernight, and the implications were
OL,8,Fenormous.
OL,10,F"What Covid proved beyond any doubt
OL,11,Fwas to expose the unsustainability of
OL,12,FWelsh rugby, as it was," says rugby
OL,13,Fjournalist Peter Jackson.
OL,15,F"Without the sort of private investors
OL,16,Ffooting the bill, then teams would
OL,17,Fhave gone bust.
