OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,FAlong with other stakeholders, the
OL,7,FUnion also sold a 14% stake in the Six
OL,8,FNations and 28% stake in the URC to
OL,9,Fprivate equity firm CVC.
OL,11,FPayments for the shares were phased.
OL,12,FThe WRU has already drawn down its
OL,13,Festimated #24 million from the URC
OL,14,Fdeal.
OL,16,FThey have also received the final
OL,17,Fpayment of the #40.5 million they
OL,18,Fearned from the Six Nations agreement.
