OL,6,FThe idea at the time would have been
OL,7,Fto invest that capital funding so that
OL,8,Fthe income of the Welsh Rugby Union
OL,9,Fbecame more diversified.
OL,11,FBut the reality of those deals is that
OL,12,Fnow the WRU is simply facing a
OL,13,Fstraight dilution of its income from
OL,14,Fthe tournaments.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, Covid hit and Covid
OL,17,Fcost us," says WRU Chair Richard
OL,18,FCollier-Keywood, who arrived at the
OL,19,FUnion after those deals were signed.
