OL,6,FUnearned Reward
OL,8,FAfter years of chaos off the field. A
OL,9,Fcrisis would soon develop on it.
OL,11,FThroughout 2023, a raft of senior
OL,12,Finternational players, the last of the
OL,13,Fgolden generation, retired almost en
OL,14,Fmasse.
OL,16,FJustin Tipuric, Dan Biggar and Alun
OL,17,FWyn Jones all called it a day. Ken
OL,18,FOwens had played his last game for
OL,19,FWales, and George North would soon
OL,20,Ffollow.
