OL,6,FIt ruthlessly exposed a flaw in the
OL,7,Fsystem that had been years in the
OL,8,Fmaking.
OL,10,F"So many players before and after that
OL,11,FWorld Cup retired, and we just had
OL,12,Fnothing else underneath," says former
OL,13,FWales fly-half James Hook.
OL,15,F"We were really enjoying the crest of
OL,16,Fa wave, and then it hit us like a ton
OL,17,Fof bricks."
