OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,FTrystan Bevan, former Head of
OL,7,FPerformance at Cardiff, said: "The
OL,8,Facademies and the regional teams were
OL,9,Fvery hard to get into and very easy to
OL,10,Fget out of.
OL,12,F"Everybody was told 'this has to
OL,13,Fsucceed otherwise none of us have got
OL,14,Fjobs'.
OL,16,F"You had to hit KPIs and standards in
OL,17,Forder to get that (Objective One)
OL,18,Ffunding continued, so that level of
OL,19,Fjeopardy was always there."
