OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,FWhen the Objective One funding ended,
OL,7,Fa national academy was set up. But
OL,8,Fthat only lasted two years before the
OL,9,Fresponsibility of developing young
OL,10,Ftalent was passed onto the four
OL,11,Fregions.
OL,13,FAt the time, it was a responsibility
OL,14,Fthey wanted in some ways. But back
OL,15,Fthen they were only given #600,000 per
OL,16,Fyear between the four of them to make
OL,17,Fit work.
