OL,3,CThe collapse of Welsh rugby: From
OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,F"What's happened, I think, is that
OL,7,Fother countries have sailed past us in
OL,8,Fterms of their investments and all the
OL,9,Fthings I've mentioned. We did not make
OL,10,Fthose in Wales in the way which we
OL,11,Fprobably should have done.
OL,13,F"And now we're in a situation where
OL,14,Fother teams have overtaken us."
OL,16,FWelsh rugby's current demise has been
OL,17,Fa decade in the making.
