OL,3,CThe collapse of Welsh rugby: From
OL,4,Cworld No.1 to 'laughing stock'
OL,6,FUntangling that web will not be
OL,7,Fstraightforward. Welsh rugby's
OL,8,Fresurrection could take another 10
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Rugby Union's next steps
OL,12,Fwill define what the sport of rugby
OL,13,Funion means to a generation of
OL,14,Fpotential fans and players in this
OL,15,Fcountry.
OL,17,FWith the national side at its lowest
OL,18,Fever ranking and the regional sides in
OL,19,Fa fight for survival - the game here
OL,20,Fhas never been in a more precarious
OL,21,Fposition.
